title: China's Wuhan city revises up total coronavirus death toll by 50 per cent
description: The COVID-19 death toll in China's Wuhan city has suddenly jumped up, with the Government revising official figures.
content:
Posted 
April 17, 2020 15:47:16
The total number of people who have died in China's Wuhan city, the epicentre of the global coronavirus outbreak, has been revised sharply up.
